### {205}{}{You know, if I wasn't obsessed with science and the prosperity of the world, I would have run away from here long ago. But now I belong here. My grave will be here. If you come out of the earth, you will return to it.}
{205}{}{你知道，如果我没有痴迷于科学和世界的繁荣，我早就逃离了这里。但现在我属于这里。我的坟墓就在这里。如果你从地球上走出来，你就会回到地球上。 -- You know, if I wasn't obsessed with science and the prosperity of the world, I would have run away from here long ago. But now I belong here. My grave will be here. If you come out of the earth, you will return to it.}
### {206}{}{What are you talking about?}
